
The Lustre filesystem is not mounted on the DGX nodes.
It can be mounted inside a Docker container with
  nscc-docker run --lustre ...

The job script submit.pbs shows an example of how to run jobs in /scratch

# copy job script into /scratch on login node
cp lustre.pbs $HOME/scratch
# change directory into /scratch
cd $(readlink $HOME/scratch)
# submit job
qsub lustre.pbs
